        "timestamp": "2019-01-28 21:35:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nI think CSITs could be submitted and the CSIT tests could be done all at once under a different ticket under the same epic (POLICY-1408).  There seems to be several tickets in that epic that touch on the APIs (ie. POLICY-1414, POLICY-1418, ..).\n\nDo you guys agree Praveen and Pam?   I could open a new ticket for CSIT coverage under POLICY-1408 and assign to Praveen?",
        "patchset_number": 5
